'''Dès Demain''' ({{IPA-fr|dɛ dəmɛ̃|lang}}; [[English language|English]]: "As of tomorrow", "Starting tomorrow"), stylized as '''¡Dès Demain!''', is a [[Social democracy|social democratic]] [[List of political parties in France|political movement in France]] founded on {{date|10 May 2017}} by [[Anne Hidalgo]], [[Christiane Taubira]] and [[Martine Aubry]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.lemonde.fr/idees/article/2017/05/10/des-demain-un-nouveau-mouvement-politique-pro-europeen-et-citoyen_5125306_3232.html|title=Dès demain, un nouveau mouvement politique pro-européen et citoyen|last=Collectif|date=2017-05-10|work=Le Monde.fr|access-date=2017-05-10|language=fr|issn=1950-6244}}</ref>

